com.googlecode.cqengine.index.support

Interface SortedKeyStatisticsIndex<A extends Comparable<A>,O>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Index<O>, KeyStatisticsIndex<A,O>, ModificationListener<O>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SortedKeyStatisticsAttributeIndex<A,O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiskIndex, NavigableIndex, OffHeapIndex, SimplifiedSQLiteIndex, SQLiteIndex

    public interface SortedKeyStatisticsIndex<A extends Comparable<A>,O>
extends KeyStatisticsIndex<A,O>
    An index which allows the set of distinct keys to be queried in sorted order, and which can return statistics on the number of objects stored for each key. Created by niall.gallagher on 09/01/2015.
